tip.text: Dunyada daha iyi hamburger olabilecegini zannetmiyorum?french fries ekleyin,diger patatesler pek guzel degil!!!on numara 5 yildiz!!!🖐⭐️💋🍻🔫
Spanish omlette sandwich is delicious!!!Good breakfast location in the heart of barcelona!✌️💃🏻💃🏻⭐️
Domatesli ekmek basarili,bikini cok guzel,hamburger lezzetli fakat bu fiyata al asador aranda da ceyrek kuzu yersiniz!!
Perfect sea food restaurant with good prize!!chipriones-lobster-muscells highly recommended!!But i was dissapointed with baby octopus it was hard and untasty!!!🐙👇🏽. 4⭐️ out of 5!!!!
